{"tid":1411010,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"今日係手持午餐肉就有閪屌既日子","createTime":"2019-08-05T02:49:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T05:48:21.000Z","uid":52013,"like":18,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2ed83b79ce283bd46f168656b7da1d09d6288f4d","tid":1411010,"uid":52013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-05T02:49:06.000Z","msg":"2012又好,927又好,UFO又好,有咩事發生都唔驚,,要鳩縮唔出街都實有得食~~<br />\n當然,,到有日真係出現 全香港範圍MAP炮 就咩都唔使<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F163932_a2cdc25e37dba43ebb1f73f9ef75e4e1.jpg&h=5f1119c2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n放在廚房櫃的鑵頭同米,[現鑵頭總存貨有$10000左右]米有50kg<br />\n由歐洲火腿,到中國午餐肉,回煱肉,,豆,菜,金寶湯<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/3dHRiV5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3dHRiV5.jpg&h=1f7d2192&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一箱箱未開太多,,放到出廳[依d全部係魚]<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/12/164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F12%2F164003_45a6f56b9383021925f49be7d93c4258.jpg&h=c2b5eae7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n水污染,未驚~~~現有16箱 1.5L X12<br />\n其實一向飲樽裝水好耐,現在D水喉水煮完都飲到唔舒服<br />\n即食面 有 5箱左右啦<br />\n<br />\n另外,,打邊爐石油氣有存貨 21支,,<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\nBY THE WAY 集會地點見</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">一、徹底撤回修例<br />\n二、收回暴動定義<br />\n三、撤銷對所有反送中抗爭者控